content:
[[module CSS]]
#page-title {
    display: none;
}

.content-panel p {
    padding: 0 0.75em;
}

#tagged-pages-list {
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
    column-width: 12rem;
    column-gap: 1.25rem;
    column-rule: 1px solid #888;
    counter-reset: index;
}
.pages-list-item {
    margin-bottom: 0.675em;
    line-height: 1.125;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: .175rem;
}
.pages-list-item::before {
    counter-increment: index;
    content: counter(index) ".";
    font-size: .625em;
    text-align: end;
    font-feature-settings: 'case','ss01','ss04','tnum';
}

.pages-tag-cloud-box {
    margin-top: -0.125rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    grid-gap: 0.185rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-block: 1.5rem;
}

#u-hidden .pages-tag-cloud-box a:not([href^="/system:page-tags/tag/_"]) { display: none; }
[[/module]]

[[div class="content-panel centered standalone"]]
Welcome to the tags page! What is a tag? Find out on our [[[a-laymen-s-guide-to-tagging|Tag Guide]]]!

You can browse tags with the [#toc0 tag cloud] at the bottom, or see a [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/tag-list comprehensive list of tags]. If you want to search for more than one tag at a time, try our advanced [[[Tag Search]]].
[[/div]]

[[module PagesByTag]]


